---
description: Drag and resize behavior rules
globs: ["src/logic/interactions/**/*", "src/components/calendar/**/*"]
alwaysApply: true
---

- Drag move:
  - modifies start/end while preserving duration.
  - snaps to 15-minute boundaries.
- Resize:
  - top handle changes start.
  - bottom handle changes end.
  - enforces minimum duration.
- Never allow invalid intervals (`end <= start`).
- Keep drag/resize math deterministic and pure where possible.
- Pointer interactions must not leave state partially updated.
